ider%20that%20the%20drones%20in%20the%20clips%20were%20equipped%20with%20higher-capacity%20batteries%20and%20more%20powerful%20video%20transmitters%20to%20extend%20their%20flight%20range.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20used%20a%20relay%20system%2C%20he%20said.%20These%20are%20a%20relatively%20new%20development%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20where%20a%20drone%20bounces%20its%20signal%20off%20another%20drone%20to%20extend%20its%20range%20to%20the%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkarlat%20said%20each%20drone%20costs%20roughly%20%24475%20to%20%24500%2C%20but%20can%20be%20sold%20for%20up%20to%20%24600%20if%20equipped%20with%20thermal%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20drones%20are%20not%20available%20to%20everyone%2C%20but%20production%20is%20scaling%20up%20every%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Skarlat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPreviously%2C%20only%20a%20few%20units%20were%20flying%20over%2040%20km.%20Now%2C%20there%20are%20already%20several%20dozen%20units%20doing%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsistent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-electronic-warfare-fight-drone-pilots-must-sort-safe-paths-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFPV%20drone%20strikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20such%20a%20range%20would%20show%20how%20the%20war%20is%20pushing%20the%20limits%20of%20the%20humble%20hobby%20drone%2C%20which%20is%20now%20inspiring%20militaries%20around%20the%20world%20to%20ramp%20up%20their%20own%20uncrewed%20aerial%20system%20arsenals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20summer%2C%20a%20drone%20unit%20in%20Zaporizhzhia%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Ronins%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20flew%20quadcopters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drones-volunteer-sternenko-donations-fpv-pilots-win-russia-war-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eup%20to%2034%20miles%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20attack%20Russian%20air%20defense%20systems%20%E2%80%94%20a%20range%20that%20was%20almost%20unheard%20of%20among%20drone