arity.%20Business%20Insider%20verified%20his%20booking%20at%20a%20Marriott%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E-%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3Elicensed%20Sonder%20property%20in%20Montreal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarriott-sonder-agreement-terminated-meltdown-unraveled-chaos-customers-help-bonvoy-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMarriott-Sonder%20breakup%3C%2Fa%3E%20put%20a%20damper%20on%20one%20of%20the%20happiest%20days%20of%20our%20lives%20%E2%80%94%20our%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20girlfriend%2C%20who%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20New%20York%2C%20told%20me%20she%20wanted%20to%20be%20someplace%20new%20when%20she%20got%20proposed%20to.%20We%20had%20heard%20a%20lot%20of%20great%20things%20about%20Montreal%2C%20so%20we%20booked%20a%20five-day%20stay%20at%20a%20Sonder%20apartment%20in%20Old%20Montreal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20proposed%20to%20her%20on%20Sunday%20at%20the%20Westmount%20Conservatory%20and%20Greenhouses%20in%20Montreal.%20It's%20a%20really%20lovely%20spot%2C%20with%20a%20beautiful%20library%2C%20greenhouse%2C%20and%20a%20little%20recreation%20area%20in%20the%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%2C%20we%20enjoyed%20the%20city%20and%20celebrated.%20We%20window-shopped%2C%20explored%20Montreal%2C%20and%20visited%20a%20fine%20art%20museum.%20We%20weren't%20glued%20to%20our%20phones%20like%20we%20are%20on%20a%20normal%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20only%20saw%20the%20email%20informing%20us%20about%20the%20Marriott-Sonder%20breakup%20after%20the%20Sonder%20worker%20came%20and%20knocked%20on%20our%20door%20at%2010%20a.m.%20on%20Monday%2C%20telling%20us%20to%20leave%20in%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f386df03-2e50-46c0-9db5-11c8f5c5933a%5C%22%3EGetting%20kicked%20out%20after%20their%20engagement%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20girlfriend%20answered%20the%20door%2C%20and%20the%20guy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20sorry%2C%20you%20guys%20need%20to%20leave.%20Your%20reservation%20is%20canceled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20ready%20to%20tear%20him%20a%20new%20one.%20I%20told%20him%20we%20had%20another%20day%20to%20go%20on%20our%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20sorry%20to%20be%20blunt%20with%20you%2C%20but%20I'm%20losing%20my%20job%20right%20now.%20My%20last%20task%20is%20to%20tell%20people%20that%20they%20need%20to%20leave.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BOK%2C%20this%20guy's%20probably%20having%20a%20worse%20day%20than%20I%20am.%26quot%3B%20So%20I%20dropped%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20immediately%20called%20Marriott%20and%20attempted%20to%20rebook.%20Marriott%20was%20able%20to%20put%20us%20up%20in%20another%20hotel%2C%20about%20a%20mile%20from%20where%20we%20were.%20But%20it%20cost%20more%20than%20the%20original%20accommodation%20by%20about%2030%20Canadian%20dollars%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eor%20about%20%2421%2C%20so%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20scam%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20your%20reservation's%20canceled%2C%20but%20we%20can%20make%20you%20a%20new%20reservation%20for%20more%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarriott%20offered%20me%20500%20points%20for%20the%20trouble%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20book%20with%20the%20hotel%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scene%20in%20the%20lobby%20afterward%20was%20something%20to%20behold.%20Everybody%20was%20down%20in%20the%20lobby%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarriott-sonder-derailed-dream-vacation-single-mother-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeverybody%20was%20pissed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Many%20had%20several%20days%20left%20before%20their%20flights%20back%20home.%20Several%20told%20us%20that%20they%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarriott-sonder-licensing-termination-guest-apartment-new-booking-how-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enever%20book%20with%20Marriott%3C%2Fa%3E%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20me%20wants%20to%20really%20go%20in