y%2C%20and%20skin%20density.%20It%20can%20also%20help%20treat%20conditions%20like%20acne%20and%20alopecia%2C%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8833aaf-1f83-4035-b940-d668af6ffb4d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20I%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20I%20tested%20red%20light%20therapy%20masks%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20out%20which%20devices%20are%20worth%20your%20money%20(and%20face)%2C%20I%20tested%20eight%20of%20the%20top-rated%20handheld%20LED%20wands%20and%20masks%20on%20the%20market%20over%20the%20course%20of%20six%20weeks%2C%20and%20consulted%20two%20dermatologists%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20a%20red%20light%20therapy%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20scientifically%20verify%20the%20efficacy%20of%20a%20single%20product%2C%20I%20evaluated%20each%20pick%20for%20comfort%2C%20LED%20strength%2C%20light%20coverage%2C%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20use%20consistently.%20I%20looked%20for%20devices%20that%20helped%20minimize%20wrinkles%2C%20improve%20rosacea%20or%20skin%20discoloration%2C%20and%20nipped%20acne%20in%20the%20bud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e68b73bd-29c2-498d-ad5e-1a70b0c9f8de%5C%22%3EThe%20best%20red%20light%20therapy%20mask%20I%20tested%3A%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f93d9ab6-dc83-43d7-ab2a-a6132c1b30f3%5C%22%3EThe%20best%20red%20light%20therapy%20wand%20I%20tested%3A%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd63d1ac-636c-45e2-89bd-c74c9379507d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Wavelengths%2C%20explained%5C%22%3EWavelengths%2C%20explained%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Wavelengths%2C%20explainedMost%20red%20light%20therapy%20devices%20actually%20leverage%20a%20range%20of%20light%20wavelengths%20to%20deliver%20more%20benefits%20to%20your%20skin.%20%20%26quot%3BThe%20wavelength%20determines%20how%20deeply%20the%20light%20penetrates%20tissue%20and%20what%20processes%20it%20influences%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Maccarone.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20skin%20health%2C%20these%20are%20the%20most%20common%3A%5C%22%3EMost%20red%20light%20therapy%20devices%20actually%20leverage%20a%20range%20of%20light%20wavelengths%20to%20deliver%20more%20benefits%20to%20your%20skin.%20%26quot%3BThe%20wavelength%20determines%20how%20deeply%20the%20light%20penetrates%20tissue%20and%20what%20processes%20it%20influences%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Maccarone.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20skin%20health%2C%20these%20are%20the%20most%20common%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlue%20light%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(380%E2%80%94500%20nm)%20stays%20close%20to%20the%20skin's%20surface%20and%20can%20target%20acne-causing%20bacteria%20to%20reduce%20breakouts%2C%20and%20help%20with%20superficial%20inflammatory%20skin%20conditions%20like%20dermatitis%2C%20eczema%2C%20and%20psoriasis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERed%20light%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(630%E2%80%94660%20nm)%20is%20absorbed%20by%20the%20skin%20and%20targets%20superficial%20concerns%20%E2%80%94%20acne%2C%20skin%20texture%2C%20skin%20elasticity%2C%20firmness.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENear-infrared%20light%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(810%E2%80%94850%20nm)%20penetrates%20deeper%2C%20reaching%20muscles%2C%20joints%2C%20bones%2C%20and%20even%20the%20brain%20%E2%80%94%20NIR%20can%20help%20athletes%20with%20muscle%20recovery%2C%20inflammation%2C%20and%20healing%20of%20injuries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20devices%20will%20also%20include%20%3Cstrong%3Egreen%20light%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(500-570%20nm)%20to%20help%20stimulate%20collagen%20production%20and%20reduce%20pigmentation%20issues%20or%20%3Cstrong%3Eamber%20light%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(570%E2%80%94600%20nm)%20which%20targets%20skin%20tone%2C%20wrinkles%2C%20and%20superficial%20inflammation%2C%20though%20not%20as%20powerfully%20as%20blue%20or%20red%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b877586-69bd-44de-82df-62d0931d8cac%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EFAQs%20on%20red%20light%20therapy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-test%3D%5C%22faq-question-field%5C%22%3EDoes%20red%20light%20therapy%20work%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScience%20says%20yes.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Research%20shows%20red%20light%20therapy%20can%20help%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC3926176%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimprove%20the%20complexion%20and%20texture%20of%20the%20skin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10311288%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimprove%20signs%20of%20aging%3C%2Fa%3E%20(firmness%2C%20elasticity%2C%20skin%20density)%2C%20help%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.prod.researchhub.com%2Fuploads%2Fpapers%2F2023%2F12%2F07%2FPhotobiomodulation.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estimulate%20skin%20rejuvenation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20help%20treat%20conditions%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.prod.researchhub.com%2Fuploads%2Fpapers%2F2023%2F12%2F07%2FPhotobiomodulation.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacne%20%2B%20alopecia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20can%20even%20help%20inflammation%2C%20pain%2C%20and%20muscle%20recovery.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBeauty%20aside%2C%20therapy%20devices%20with%20a%20near-infrared%20light%20wavelength%20can%20support%20wound%20healing%2C%20reduces%20inflammation%2C%20and%20can%20improve%20joint%20stiffness%2C%20muscle%20recovery%2C%20and%20chronic%20pain%2C%20Dr.%20Maccarone%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-test%3D%5C%22faq-question-field%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20red%20light%20therapy%20benefit%20my%20skin%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20tells%20your%20skin%20cells%20to%20get%20to%20work.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Red%20light%20therapy%20works%20by%20stimulating%20your%20cells'%20energy%20producers%2C%20mitochondria%2C%20which%20then%20means%20your%20cells%20have%20more%20energy%20and%20do%20more%20of%20what%20they%20do%20best%3A%20repair%20damage%20faster%2C%20produce%20more%20collagen%2C%20increase%20circulation%2C%20and%20reduce%20inflammation%2C%20Dr.%20Maccarone%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20targets%20signs%20of%20aging%20and%20skin%20conditions.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Once%20your%20skin%20cells%20are%20told%20to%20get%20to%20work%2C%20the%20result%20of%20these%20biological%20processes%20is%20improving%20concerns%20like%20fine%20lines%2C%20wrinkles%2C%20skin%20texture%2C%20skin%20discoloration%2C%20and%20acne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20stronger%20the%20device%2C%20the%20better%20and%20faster%20it'll%20work.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20more%20powerful%20a%20therapy%20device%2C%20the%20better%20it'll%20deliver%20results%20over%20a%20shorter%20period%20of%20time.%20For%20example%2C%20our%20top%20pick%20for%20the%20best%20red%20light%20therapy%20mask%20is%20the%20TheraFace%20Pro%2C%20which%20has%20504%20lights%20and%20only%20needs%20four%20minutes%20on%20each%20light%20wavelength%20for%20therapeutic%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-test%3D%5C%22faq-question-field%5C%22%3EIs%20red%20light%20therapy%20safe%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYes%2C%20red%20light%20therapy%20is%20safe.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BBecause%20LEDs%20do%20not%20produce%20ultraviolet%20radiation%2C%20they%20are%20considered%20a%20safer%20form%20of%20light%20therapy%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%2C%20it%20doesn't%20cause%20cancer.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Red%20light%20therapy%20devices%20don't%20emit%20ultraviolet%20(UV)%20light%2C%20which%20is%20the%20primary%20cause%20of%20skin%20cancer.%20And%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0022202X16324824%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%20have%20shown%3C%2Fa%3E%20these%20devices%20don't%20damage%20DNA%20or%20cause%20mutations%20of%20your%20skin%20cells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStill%2C%20talk%20to%20your%20doctor%20if%20you're%20on%20medications%20or%20have%20a%20condition%20that%20makes%20your%20skin%20more%20sensitive%20to%20light.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20you%20take%20any%20medication%20that%20increases%20your%20sensitivity%20to%20the%20sun%20(like%20certain%20antibiotics%2C%20cardiovascular%20drugs%2C%20or%20diuretics)%2C%20you%20have%20a%20skin%20condition%20that%20causes%20photosensitivity%2C%20or%20a%20history%20of%20skin%20cancer%2C%20talk%20to%20your%20dermatologist%20before%20you%20start%20using%20a%20red%20light%20therapy%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-test%3D%5C%22faq-question-field%5C%22%3EHow%20effective%20is%20red%20light%20therapy%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20depends%20on%20your%20consistency%20and%20other%20skincare%20habits.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20At-home%20red%20light%20therapy%20devices%20can%20definitely%20improve%20skin%20health%2C%20but%20the%20results%20may%20also%20be%20temporary%20depending%20on%20your%20age%2C%20sun%20exposure%20levels%2C%20and%20habits%20like%20alcohol%20and%20tobacco%20use%2C%20Dr.%20Camp%20points%20out.%20Some%20ways%20you%20can%20maximize%20your%20potential%20benefits%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUsing%20other%20forms%20of%20skin%20therapy%2C%20like%20microcurrent%20and%20EMS%20devices%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFollowing%20a%20regular%2C%20anti-aging%20skincare%20routine%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-sunscreen-moisturizer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edaily%20SPF%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fretinol-vs-retin-a-vs-retinoid%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretinol%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20other%20active%20ingredients%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-vitamin-c-serum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evitamin%20C%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUsing%20the%20device%20consistently%20(Dr.%20Camp%20says%20you%20should%20start%20to%20see%20results%20after%20two%20or%20more%20months)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20depends%20on%20the%20red%20light%20therapy%20device.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20red%20light%20therap