n't%20irritate%20any%20pressure%20points%20against%20my%20face.%20Moreover%2C%20I%20found%20the%20comprehensive%20coverage%20worth%20the%20slight%20stuffiness%3A%20Other%20red%20light%20therapy%20masks%20with%20nose%20and%20mouth%20cutouts%20might%20be%20more%20comfortable%2C%20but%20the%20Mask%20Glo's%20added%20coverage%20ensures%20a%20more%20targeted%20light%20on%20fine-line-prone%20areas%20like%20the%20eyes%2C%20mouth%2C%20and%20jawline%20%E2%80%94%20a%20worthy%20trade-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20uses%20504%20LED%20lights%20and%20three%20different%20light%20wavelengths.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Mask%20Glo%20uses%20far%2C%20far%20more%20lights%20than%20any%20other%20mask%20I%20tested%20(except%20the%20original%20TheraFace%20Mask)%2C%20meaning%20it's%20more%20powerful%20within%20a%20shorter%20time%20period.%20One%20session%20runs%20through%20four%20minutes%20of%20red%20light%2C%20four%20minutes%20of%20red%20%2B%20infrared%20light%2C%20and%20four%20minutes%20of%20blue%20light%20to%20target%20fine%20lines%2C%20skin%20discoloration%2C%20superficial%20inflammation%2C%20and%20acne%2C%20for%2012%20minutes%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20holding%20and%20wearing%20a%20red%20light%20therapy%20mask%20from%20Therabody.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6914fcf4e1a9cbb014de17cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20head%20straps%20are%20equipped%20with%20vibration%20technology%20for%20a%20gentle%20scalp%20massage.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20don't%20have%20to%20wear%20it%20for%20long.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Other%20masks%20use%2020%2B%20minute%20cycles%2C%20but%20the%20Mask%20Glo's%2012%20minute%20cycle%20was%20short%20enough%20that%20I%20could%20wear%20it%20while%20I%20was%20making%20breakfast%2C%20or%20pop%20it%20on%20during%20my%20nightly%20routine%20before%20getting%20into%20bed.%20This%2012%20minute%20cycle%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20put%20on%20out%20of%20habit%2C%20which%20Dr.%20Maccarone%20says%20a%20genuine%20key%20aspect%20in%20a%20red%20light%20therapy%20tools'%20efficacy.%20It's%20worth%20noting%20that%20with%20this%20mask%2C%20you%20can't%20just%20do%20a%20single%20four-minute%20cycle%20of%20just%20one%20type%20of%20light%20(if%2C%20say%2C%20you%20only%20want%20blue%20light%20acne%20treatment%20on%20a%20timecrunch).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20lightweight%2C%20secure%20on%20your%20head%2C%20and%20cordless%20for%20easy%20movement.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It's%20pretty%20lightweight%20at%20just%20514%20grams%20(that's%2062%20grams%20less%20than%20the%20more%20expensive%20TheraFace%20Mask%2C%20often%20cited%20as%20annoyingly%20heavy).%20It%20also%20uses%20a%20cordless%20dual%20headstrap%20system%20to%20go%20over%20the%20top%20and%20across%20the%20back%20of%20your%20head%2C%20which%20helped%20me%20feel%20secure%20when%20walking%20around%20with%20the%20mask%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20designed%20to%20protect%20your%20eyes%20from%20the%20light.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhereas%20many%20of%20the%20masks%20I%20tested%20blinded%20my%20periphery%20with%20red%20light%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Df50d702ee744177944339aa2743a31acf75e381cf45b8f4abcb3a2ef77a12e04%26postID%3D6914c5c1161796b7bedced25%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fbest-red-light-therapy-mask%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.therabody.com%252Fproducts%252Ftheraface-mask-glo-led-light-mask%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETheraFace%20Mask%20Glo%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20designed%20with%20a%20protective%20eye%20shield%20layer%20in%20order%20to%20widen%20your%20field%20of%20vision.%20This%20allowed%20me%20to%20see%20relatively%20well%20even%20as%20I%20watched%20TV%20or%20walked%20around%20my%20house%20(though%20it%20was%20a%20little%20nauseating%20try