rsltid%253DAfmBOorXqQNMOqJMx2wmUn1ryTTNk5HWK1Yr5A2eAi-bphVxKVjVzELL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclinical%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20over%20100%20participants%20of%20varying%20skin%20tones%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20were%20middle%20aged%20(though%20this%20study%20hasn't%20been%20peer-reviewed%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20has%20biased%20funding).%20The%20subjects%20used%20the%20Mask%20Glo%20for%2012%20weeks%20and%20largely%20found%20that%20it%20improved%20their%20skin%20tone%20evenness%2C%20radiance%2C%20dark%20spots%2C%20fine%20lines%2C%20and%20wrinkles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf398ce5-c11f-477e-bc15-9336e2205b17%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20red%20light%20therapy%20wand%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20best%20red%20light%20therapy%20wand%3A%20Medicube%20Booster%20Pro%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20holding%20up%20a%20red%20light%20therapy%20wand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6914fd9d89026fbb4d0d88c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20K-beauty%20favorite%20is%20lightweight%20and%20has%20a%20microcurrent%20mode%20for%20sculpting.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20best%20red%20light%20therapy%20wand%20%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20uses%20five%20light%20wavelength%20treatments%20to%20target%20signs%20of%20aging.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20wands%20that%20promise%20red%20light%20therapy%20benefits%2C%20the%20Medicube%20Age-R%20Booster%20Pro%20stands%20out%20for%20delivering%20bigger%20results.%20This%20K-beauty%20device%20uses%20five%20different%20LED%20wavelengths%2C%20including%20red%2C%20infrared%2C%20and%20blue%2C%20to%20target%20fine%20lines%2C%20uneven%20tone%2C%20and%20skin%20laxity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20also%20delivers%20six%20skin-boosting%20treatments%20for%20a%20full%20at-home%20facial.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Booster%20Pro%20stands%20above%20other%20red%20light%20wands%20because%20it's%20a%20complete%20skincare%20tool.%20Besides%20light%20therapy%2C%20it%20combines%20six%20skin-enhancing%20technologies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20microcurrent%2C%20EMS%2C%20electroporation%2C%20and%20electric%20%26quot%3Bneedles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Dr.%20Camp%20explains%2C%20adding%20modalities%20like%20these%20to%20your%20skincare%20routine%20can%20help%20amplify%20the%20effects%20of%20red%20light%20therapy%20over%20time.%20While%20red%20light%20therapy%20won't%20give%20you%20instant%20results%2C%20these%20other%20treatments%20will%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20found%20my%20skin%20did%20feel%20slightly%20tighter%20and%20more%20hydrated%20after%20using%20the%20air%20shot%2C%20booster%2C%20and%20microcurrent%20modes.%20For%20%24220%2C%20you're%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20in%20one%20sleek%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20red%20light%20therapy%20is%20pretty%20straight-forward%20and%20seemingly%20effective.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20found%20the%20red%20light%20therapy%20Derma-S%20Mode%20super%20simple%20to%20use%20%E2%80%94%20you%20pick%20your%20mode%2C%20pick%20your%20intensity%2C%20and%20then%20make%20contact%20with%20your%20skin.%20This%20is%20just%20like%20every%20other%20mode%2C%20except%20you%20don't%20feel%20anything%20when%20the%20program%20starts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fage-r-medicube-digital-clinic%2Fid1610283967%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccompanying%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20an%208-minute%20facial%20routine%20video%20that%20I%20found%20to%20be%20super%20comprehensive%20in%20helping%20me%20cover%20every%20corner%20of%20my%20face%20that%20could%20possibly%20have%20fine%20lines.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20do%20wish%20there%20was%20more%20real-time%20feedback%20that%20I%20was%20%26quot%3Bdoing%20it%20right%26quot%3B%20(the%20device%20blinks%20when%20in%20contact%20with%20your%20skin%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20see%20this%20unless%20you're%20looking%20in%20a%20mirror)%20or%20perhaps%20a%20step-by-step%20guided%20tutorial%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20radius%20of%20the%20light%20is%20quite%20small.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20more%20hands%20on%20%E2%80%94%20but%20more%20versatile%20%E2%80%94%20than%20a%20red%20light%20therapy%20mask.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20a%20red%20light%20therapy%20mask%20is%20great%20for%20no-effort%20sessions%2C%20the%20Medicube%20Booster%20Pro%20gives%20you%20way%20more%20tools%20for%20your%20money%2C%20including%20easy-to-use%20red%20and%20near-infrared%20light%20therapy.%20For%20slightly%20less%20than%20most%20LED%20masks%2C%20this%20wand%20offers%20six%20distinct%20treatments%20in%20one%20sleek%2C%20portable%20wand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20it%20requires%20more%20engagement%20%E2%80%94%20you%20have%20to%20actively%20move%20it%20across%20your%20face%20and%20remember%20what%20ground%20you've%20haven't%20covered%20yet.%20And%20if%20you%20just%20want%20to%20lay%20there%20while%20the%20device%20works%2C%20you'll%20be%20happier%20with%20a%20mask.%20But%20the%20wand's%20mobility%20also%20means%20you%20can%20use%20it%20to%20precisely%20target%20the%20area%20that%20need%20it%20most%2C%20like%20under%20your%20eyes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20areas%20outside%20your%20face%2C%20like%20acne%20on%20the%20chest%20or%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20travel-friendly%20and%20surprisingly%20easy%20to%20use.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Medicube%20Booster%20Pro%20seemed%20pretty%20intimidating%20to%20me%20at%20first%2C%20with%20its%20six%20different%20functions%20and%20four%20treatment%20mode.%20But%20after%20I%20had%20a%20few%20treatments%20under%20my%20belt%2C%20it%20all%20became%20pretty%20intuitive.%20The%20on-device%20LED%20screen%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20toggle%20between%20modes%2C%20adjust%20intensity%20levels%2C%20and%20track%20treatment%20time.%20It's%20comfortable%20to%20hold%20and%20pack%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-travel-makeup-bag%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20makeup%20bag%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20definitely%20helps%20with%20consistent%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20from%20Medicube%20app%2C%20the%20author%20using%20the%20Medicube%20wand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691503d089026fbb4d0d8970%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20used%20the%20Medicube%20Booster%20Pro%20in%20tandem%20with%20its%20companion%20app%2C%20which%20notified%20me%20every%20time%20I%20was%20due%20for%20treatment.%3Cp%3EMedicube%2C%20Rachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20companion%20app%20helps%20keep%20you%20consistent%20%E2%80%94%20though%20it%20could%20be%20more%20guided%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20The%20accompanying%20Age-R%20app%20helped%20me%20remember%20what%20mode%20did%20what%20and%20how%20exactly%20to%20apply%20the%20treatment%2C%20and%20was%20a%20key%20component%20of%20boosting%20my%20confidence%20with%20the%20wand.%20It%20even%20creates%20a%20personalized%20skincare%20calendar%20for%20which%20modes%20you%20should%20use%20when%20and%20how%20often.%20There%20are%20video%20tutorials%20for%20each%20setting%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Shorts%20where%20content%20creators%20share%20their%20full%20routine%20for%2C%20say%2C%20elasticity%20care%20in%20your%2040s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20especially%20appreciated%20the%20push%20notification%20reminders%20to%20keep%20me%20on%20track%20with%20my%20Booster%20Pro%20calendar%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20option%20to%20upload%20before-and-after%20photos%20to%20see%20if%20regular%20use%20is%20actually%20working.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20app%20could%20do%20more%20to%20walk%20you%20through%20each%20session%20in%20real-time.%20Competitor%20apps%20like%20Therabody's%20offer%20guided%20%26quot%3Bfacial%20workouts%26quot%3B%20with%20beeps%20and%20prompts%20to%20change%20location.%20The%20Booster%20Pro%20app%20doesn't%20offer%20much%20in%20the%20way%20of%20sensory%20expectation%3B%20I%20found%20myself%20Googling%20and%20digging%20through%20community%20forums%20to%20confirm%20whether%20the%20prickly%20sensation%20was%20normal%20(and%20indeed%20it%20was).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20is%20a%20learning%20curve%20with%20some%20modes.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20someone%20who%20hasn't%20used%20microcurrent%20or%20microneedling%20devices%20before%20%E2%80%94%20or%20done%20any%20skincare%20regularly%20beyond%20my%20basic%20anti-aging%20daily%20routine%20%E2%80%94%20I%20found%20some%20of%20the%20advanced%20functions%20like%20EMS%20and%20electroporation%20a%20little%20jarring%20at%20first%2C%20as%20they%20gently%20zapped%20or%20tingled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20couldn't%20remember%20which%20mode%20required%20certain%20products%20(Medicube's%20Booster%20mode%20works%20best%20with%20a%20serum%20or%20ampoule%2C%20while%20the%20MC%20and%20Derma%20Shot%20modes%20are%20better%20after%20your%20regular%20skincare)%20and%20which%20didn't%20(like%20Air%20Shot).%20After%20about%20a%20week%20of%20regularly%20using%20the%20device%20and%20its%20many%20treatments%2C%20it%20finally%20started%20to%20click.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5af7fd5-04ab-47bd-af01-a84d81bd267d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20mask%20runner-up%5C%22%3EThe%20best%20runner-up%20red%20light%20therapy%20mask%3A%20Dr.%20Dennis%20Gross%20DRx%20SpectraLite%20FaceWare%20Pro%20LED%20Device%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20wearing%20a%20rose%20gold%20red%20light%20therapy%20mask.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6914ff42e1a9cbb014de1808%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20delivers%20four%20types%20of%20light%20therapy%20in%20just%203%20minutes%20each.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Dr.%20Dennis%20Gross%20DRx%20SpectraLite%20FaceWare%20Pro%20LED%20Device%20uses%20100%20red%20and%2062%20blue%20LED%20lights%20(162%20in%20total)%20to%20emit%20near-infrared%2C%20red%2C%20blue%2C%20and%20amber%20wavelengths.%20This%20means%20it%20targets%20wrinkles%2C%20sun%20damage%2C%20and%20acne%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20option%20to%20run%20through%20a%20cycle%20of%20red%2C%20blue%2C%20amber%2C%20and%20near-infrared%20together%20(or%20a%20combination%20of%20all).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20session%20lasts%20just%20three%20minutes%2C%20which%20is%20undeniably%20appealing%20for%20anyone%20trying%20to%20build%20this%20into%20an%20already-loaded%20skincare%20routine.%20That%20said%2C%20with%20under%20100%20of%20each%20type%20of%20LED%20light%2C%20I'm%20skeptical%20of%20how%20effective%20the%20shorter%20cycle%20is%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20I%20know%2C%20per%20our%20dermatologists%2C%20that%20consistency%20is%20more%20important%20than%20duration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20incredibly%20lightweight%2C%20breathable%2C%20and%20offers%20great%20coverage.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20pros%20to%20this%20mask%20is%20the%20strategically%20vented%20plastic%20shell%2C%20which%20has%20multiple%20cutouts%20to%20shed%20weight%20and%20make%20the%20mask%20more%20breathable.%20I%20worried%20this%20would%20compromise%20where%20exactly%20the%20light%20was%20hitting%2C%20but%20the%20openings%20are%20designed%20thoughtfully%3A%20The%20eye%20slits%20arch%20up%20so%20you%20can%20see%2C%20but%20the%20light%20still%20hits%20the%20crow's%20feet%20area.%20While%20the%20mouth%20opening%20didn't%20line%20up%20perfectly%20for%20me%2C%20the%20angle%20of%20the%20surrounding%20LEDs%20still%20hit%20my%20chin%20and%20smile%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20I%20felt%20the%20areas%20I%20wanted%20targeted%20on%20my%20face%20%3Cem%3Ewere%3C%2Fem%3E%20being%20targeted%2C%20and%20the%20lighter%20weight%20and%20contoured%20fit%20made%20it%20comfortable%20to%20wear%20with%20no%20weird%20pressure%20points.%20But%20because%20it's%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20mask%20with%20a%20rigid%20shape%2C%20fit%20and%20coverage%20may%20vary%20person%20to%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20doesn't%20cover%20the%20neck%2C%20and%20the%20head%20strap%20could%20be%20more%20secure.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20neck%20lines%20or%20tech%20neck%20are%20your%20concern%2C%20skip%20this%20mask.%20Fit-wise%2C%20it%20uses%20a%20single%20silicone%20trap%20that%20goes%20around%20the%20back%20of%20the%20head%20(rather%20than%20also%20over%20the%20top).%20While%20I%20appreciated%20how%20this%20didn't%20pull%20any%20hairs%2C%20it%20did%20slip%20a%20little%20while%20I%20wore%20it.%20The%20cycle%20is%20short%20enough%20that%20this%20wasn't%20a%20dealbreaker%2C%20but%20I%20did%20have%20to%20readjust%20it%20once%20or%20twice%20over%20just%20three%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAt%20night%2C%20the%20lights%20feel%20intense%20and%20your%20vision%20is%20limited.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20a%20three%20minute%20cycle%2C%20this%20isn't%20a%20dealbreaker.%20If%20you%20pop%20this%20on%20at%20the%20start%20of%20your%20workday%20or%20while%20waiting%20for%20coffee%20to%20brew%2C%20it'll%20work%20great.%20But%20if%20you're%20like%20me%20and%20only%20practice%20self-care%20while%20laying%20on%20a%20couch%20in%20the%20evenings%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20eye%20rim%20shield%20and%20extremely%20bright%20lights%20mask%20does%20impede%20your%20vision%2C%20in%20a%20way%20that%20may%20make%20you%20less%20likely%20to%20use%20it%20consistently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22372f0e23-55d2-49c9-ba94-0e928f7e9112%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%20red%20light%20therapy%20wand%5C%22%3EThe%20best%20budget%20red%20light%20therapy%20wand%3A%20Pure%20Daily%20Care%20Luma%20Skin%20Therapy%20Wand%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20holdin