e%20majority%20also%20leverage%20near-infrared%20(810-850)%20and%20blue%20light%20(380%E2%80%94500%20nm)%20to%20cover%20both%20deeper%20issues%20like%20inflammation%20and%20more%20surface-level%20issues%20like%20acne-causing%20bacteria.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfortable%20design%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Depending%20on%20material%2C%20shape%2C%20coverage%2C%20and%20contouring%2C%20each%20mask%20will%20fit%20differently%20and%20each%20wand%20will%20feel%20different%20in%20hand.%20The%20best%20red%20light%20therapy%20masks%20will%20have%20an%20adjustable%20head%20strap%2C%20be%20shaped%20to%20ergonomically%20curve%20around%20your%20face%2C%20and%20be%20designed%20for%20breathing%20room%20and%20no%20hotspots.%20Wands%20should%20be%20lightweight%20enough%20to%20hold%20for%20the%20entire%20treatment%2C%20comfortable%20against%20your%20skin%2C%20and%2C%20ideally%2C%20cover%20a%20large%20surface%20area.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESerums%20and%20other%20products%20needed%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Red%20light%20therapy%20devices%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20are%20all%20used%20on%20clean%2C%20dry%20skin.%20That%20said%2C%20for%20a%20device%20with%20microcurrent%2C%20you%20will%20want%20to%20apply%20a%20conductive%2C%20water-based%20gel%20or%20serum%20so%20the%20current%20can%20pass%20easily%20through%20to%20your%20skin.%20Some%20devices%2C%20like%20TheraFace%20PRO%2C%20come%20with%20a%20conductor%2C%20while%20others%2C%20like%20the%20Medicube%20Age-R%20Booster%20Pro%2C%20recommend%20using%20your%20own%20serum%20or%20occlusive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEasy%20to%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EConsistent%20use%20is%20essential%20to%20how%20effective%20a%20device%20will%20be%2C%20Dr.%20Maccarone%20says.%20If%20a%20mask%20is%20uncomfortable%20or%20a%20wand's%20treatment%20time%20is%20too%20long%2C%20you're%20less%20likely%20to%20use%20it%20regularly%20and%20see%20an%20effect.%20Consider%20what%20features%20and%20limitations%20are%20realistic%20for%20your%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fli%