-dimensional%20landscape%20structure%20that%20interconnects%20two%20or%20more%20previously%20linked%20areas%20of%20animal%20habitats%E2%80%9D.%20These%20enable%20the%20animals%20to%20disperse%2C%20reduce%20their%20risk%20of%20separation%20and%20make%20habitat%20rehabilitation%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20explored%20how%20anthropogenic%20stress%2C%20the%20development%20of%20roads%20and%20railways%2C%20and%20hydroelectric%20projects%20are%20hampering%20these%20corridors.%20The%20problem%20is%20compounded%20by%20multiple%20forests%20being%20turned%20into%20croplands%20by%20the%20farming%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-500x417.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20walking%20bear%20cubs%20to%20reintroducing%20orphaned%20elephant%20calves%20back%20into%20the%20wild%2C%20Vivek%20Menon%20is%20championing%20wildlife%20conservation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-500x417.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-300x250.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-768x641.jpeg%20768w